Domino, be ne di ci te
be ne di ci te ge//
& frigus Domino be ne di ci te
be ne di ci te lux & tenebrae Domino
date & super exaltate eum in secula
be ne di ci te coeli
be ne di ci te stellae
imber & ros Domino be ne di ci te

Note.EditorialCommentary: MS correction mark in source [which exemplar?]
Corrected to C by hand in one exemplar

According to the (closely related) printed sources, T and D here restate the imitative entries of B and A (mm. 110-11) in reverse (T=A, D=B), a combination which produces a contrapuntal error at the start of m. 115; hence the present emendation.
